Trim the @cucumber{1} and chop into thirds.

Chop the @tomato{2} into 2cm chunks.

Pop the cucumber and tomato into a #bowl{} and season to taste with @salt{to taste} and @pepper{to taste}.

Cut the @Greek Style Cheese{100%grams} into 2cm cubes.

Take half the @bamboo skewers{4} and halve widthways with the help of a #scissors{}.

Thread @olives{2%sachets}, tomatoes, Greek style cheese and cucumber pieces onto each skewer.

Repeat until you've used all your skewers and all your veg.

Serve the skewers on #platters{}.

Finish with a drizzle of @green pesto{30%grams} and @balsamic glaze{1%sachet}.

> These Mediterranean-inspired skewers are filled with flavour. In just one bite you'll find the refreshment of cucumber, the saltiness of olives and the creamy texture of Greek style cheese.